highlights.text: “Mess Around (Baby Baby)” by Rivo and Jaquet is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Australia, up 9 spots at #55.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs Australia. “Golden” is the highest at #5.
